snippet.title: ⭐ Shelly's Scratch Cards ⭐
snippet.description:
Hi 🙋‍♀️ my name is shelly, on my channel I do weekly:

* free giveaways
* live streams
* group scratches 
* live quizs
* free scratch card roulette where I pick players out of live chat
* a monthly special for my members where 1 gets picked to win a bunch of cards 🥳🥳

If you would like to join my channel as a member here is the link ❤ 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3F4-5oYNyZKph0Ldztb4vQ/join

if you would like to contact me my email address is:

shellysscratchcards@hotmail.com 


finally I just want to say a big thank you for supporting my channel, don't forget to hit the bell so you don't miss anything! take care and stay safe xxx❤️
